Enum Class ProfessionOID

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<ProfessionOID>
de.gematik.bbriccs.fhir.vzd.valueset.ProfessionOID
All Implemented Interfaces:
FromValueSet, Serializable, Comparable<ProfessionOID>, Constable
@Deprecated(since="0.5.0", forRemoval=true) public enum ProfessionOID extends Enum<ProfessionOID> implements FromValueSet
Deprecated, for removal: This API element is subject to removal in a future version.
The enumeration names are NOT translated to english to avoid confusion and translation errors.

However, to avoid german umlaute and long recurrent terms some of them are abbreviated as follows

  • BS: Betriebsstätte
  • BW: Bundeswehr
  • KTR: Kostenträger
  • LEO: Leistungserbringerorganisation
  • BV: Bundesvereinigung
